[] - User can create, read, update and delete an order

Interface:
- User can view order form 
- User can submit order form
- User can edit order 
- User can delete/cancel order 

User class
    x attributes => name, password
    x user signs up/logs in 
    x has many orders 

User controller and views
    x '/users/signup' => renders sign up form
    x '/users/signup' => processes sign up form, creates user, post
    x '/users/login' => renders login form 
    x '/users/login' => processes login form, post 
    x need to set sessions
    x user can view their orders, '/users/:id/orders'

Orders class
    x attributes => address, item, item_price, total
    x order belongs to user

Order controller and views
    x '/orders/new => renders new order form
    x '/orders' => submits order 
    x '/orders' => renders all orders
    x '/orders/:id => renders one instance
    x '/orders/:id/edit => renders update form for an instance
    x '/orders/:id => updates instance, patch 
    - '/orders/:id:/delete' => deletes instance


where to start?

